{"sha": "be921b8bbe2be2820ceb82d141762c924402c8b9", "node_id": "C_kwDOCOvoetoAKGJlOTIxYjhiYmUyYmUyODIwY2ViODJkMTQxNzYyYzkyNDQwMmM4Yjk", "commit": {"author": {"name": "Paul", "email": "baconpaul@users.noreply.github.com", "date": "2023-09-20T12:12:06Z"}, "committer": {"name": "GitHub", "email": "noreply@github.com", "date": "2023-09-20T12:12:06Z"}, "message": "Modern retrig-from-zero sample offset (#7218)\n\nThe modern 2-point DPW algorithm uses points at phase, phase-d and\r\nphase -2d to calculate. This has the defacto one-sample latency\r\neffect (at the oversample sample rate).\r\n\r\nThis doesn't matter *except* in the retrigger-from-zero case when\r\nthat shift makes the first output point at the wrong phase.\r\n\r\nSo in retrigger, intiialize phase to dphase, not to 0, so you\r\ncan hit the zero point for symmetric waveforms exactly.\r\n\r\nAddresses https://github.com/surge-synthesizer/surge-rack/issues/937", "tree": {"sha": "225fa67a64ba8aba2576ee3b314d7c227f89d867", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/surge-synthesizer/surge/git/trees/225fa67a64ba8aba2576ee3b314d7c227f89d867"}, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/surge-synthesizer/surge/git/commits/be921b8bbe2be2820ceb82d141762c924402c8b9", "comment_count": 0, "verification": {"verified": true, "reason": "valid", "signature": "-----BEGIN PGP SIGNATURE-----\n\nwsBcBAABCAAQBQJlCuGWCRBK7hj4Ov3rIwAANa4IAIfB+NqGobLxUyB7/SwCWpC+\nkVYzWkJj4HZdoT8JkE4563yqXXquWfSW66aWrUN4jDldA+dilxwPRvjBdVresSyn\nWpyuK01nYuQ5QEiZYNUkGMGTLR01cZsN/h4V/f21uZRlJPzS3bMgg7CLfmZragsU\nXcBtqKYWAkRFn/ixbbfJE8Fpq3/+Gin1jWP966VdASt+4NPpyYFMYyg+2Z50dssR\nXopCb9Kp9vlqowHNUepzCeVNNWkp4aJCd+sfoqWb/I7pIV/qQG7rL7IeIy8Ot8c9\nh163M7AqJ0OKDfZ0Gkpg1YCawtbwBFpr5eTqV1AAqtP2EeGHwJ/cJ0PT9t27R54=\n=dWfp\n-----END PGP SIGNATURE-----\n", "payload": "tree 225fa67a64ba8aba2576ee3b314d7c227f89d867\nparent f005fe72ee065aff0cc334f430755d12a806b73f\nauthor Paul <baconpaul@users.noreply.github.com> 1695211926 -0400\ncommitter GitHub <noreply@github.com> 1695211926 -0400\n\nModern retrig-from-zero sample offset (#7218)\n\nThe modern 2-point DPW algorithm uses points at phase, phase-d and\r\nphase -2d to calculate. This has the defacto one-sample latency\r\neffect (at the oversample sample rate).\r\n\r\nThis doesn't matter *except* in the retrigger-from-zero case when\r\nthat shift makes the first output point at the wrong phase.\r\n\r\nSo in retrigger, intiialize phase to dphase, not to 0, so you\r\ncan hit the zero point for symmetric waveforms exactly.\r\n\r\nAddresses https://github.com/surge-synthesizer/surge-rack/issues/937"}}, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/surge-synthesizer/surge/commits/be921b8bbe2be2820ceb82d141762c924402c8b9", "html_url": "https://github.com/surge-synthesizer/surge/commit/be921b8bbe2be2820ceb82d141762c924402c8b9", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/surge-synthesizer/surge/commits/be921b8bbe2be2820ceb82d141762c924402c8b9/comments", "author": {"login": "baconpaul", "id": 13387561, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjEzMzg3NTYx", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/13387561?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/baconpaul", "html_url": "https://github.com/baconpaul", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/baconpaul/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/baconpaul/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/baconpaul/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/baconpaul/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/baconpaul/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/baconpaul/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/baconpaul/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/baconpaul/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/baconpaul/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "committer": {"login": "web-flow", "id": 19864447, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjE5ODY0NDQ3", "avatar_url": "https